{"tid":2083304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見咁多藍絲傳媒都用外國有叛國罪黎證明立國安法係冇問題，有啲嘢想問下","createTime":"2020-06-28T15:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T18:29:40.000Z","uid":209773,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7a07de91f47489cbc9f15b833bc141cf72a94956","tid":2083304,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"利申先，唔熟法律，有錯請糾正<br />\n首先，香港本身已經有叛國罪。而叛國罪同國安法睇落最大差別就係''敵人''，要犯叛國罪就先要兩國宣戰緊。而中國係唔會同英美宣戰，所以叛國罪基本上係廢。<br />\n<br />\n但國安法就只係指勾結外國勢力，個範圍闊咗好多。咁我想問下外國事實上係咪真係有&quot;國安法&quot;針對勾結外國勢力的行為？如果有，有冇關於檢控嘅數據？因為我見啲藍媒大多數都係講外國有叛國罪，而兩條法例完全唔同。<br />\n<br />\n例如 白粉報<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200524/bkn-20200524112547075-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200524%2Fbkn-20200524112547075-0524_00822_001.html&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8ZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=2e1e7381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200524/bkn-20200524112547075-0524_00822_001.html</a> 港版國安法：外國設多條國安法 在美犯叛國罪可判死"},{"pid":"b876eb575fe0642ffeea5e2579f0c8137f5f95a4","tid":2083304,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5be6237553a4361f4b2a0d28afb035df4e15992","tid":2083304,"uid":92448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"人地民選國家, 完"},{"pid":"6b48ab5e76b7c80d29339d50b32bb6548caef606","tid":2083304,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"支那黨國不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33058d730712d1e6760992b8f78c31c57d879661","tid":2083304,"uid":209773,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5be6237553a4361f4b2a0d28afb035df4e15992","tid":2083304,"uid":92448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:15:58.000Z",